#: 03.3-Stretching-Samples.md:48 03.4-Enveloped-Samples.md:17
#: 03.5-Partial-Samples.md:9 A.03-coded-beats.md:33 A.12-sample-slicing.md:22
#: A.20-creative-coding-in-the-classroom.md:185
