#, no-wrap
msgid "sample :drum_cymbal_open, attack: 0.01, sustain: 0.3, release: 0.1"
msgstr "sample :drum_cymbal_open, attack: 0.01, sustain: 0.3, release: 0.1"

#: 03.4-Enveloped-Samples.md:124
